  [ Julien Cristau ]
  * debian/rules: RIP lpia.

  [ Cyril Brulebois ]
  * Cherry-pick from upstream (thanks to Dave Airlie for the hint):
    - radeon: fix build on non-KMS systems.
    This fixes the FTBFS on GNU/kFreeBSD.
