  * Rename "GGIMesa"-references in src/GGI/default/Makefile.am to
    "MesaGGI", which makes the package build again with newer libtool.
    (Closes: #213836)

 -- Steinar H. Gunderson <sesse@debian.org>  Sun, 15 Feb 2004 17:37:08 +0100

